h]]||{{flagu|Great Britain}}||1955-2001 (as The Haunted Swing) 2002|| In house\n|-\n|Feng Ju Palace(Wind Home Palace)||[[Phantasialand]]||{{flagu|Germany}}||2002||[[Vekoma]]\n|-\n|[[Hotel Embrujado (Haunted Hotel)]]||[[Parque Warner Madrid]]||{{flagu|Spain}}||2002||[[Vekoma]]\n|-\n|Magic House (Formally: Mad House)||[[Gardaland]]||{{flagu|Italy}}||2002||[[Vekoma]]\n|-\n|Noah\u2019s Incredible Adventure||[[Noah\u2019s Ark Water Park]]||{{flagu|United States}}||2003\u20132008||[[Mack Rides]]\n|- \n|Verlies des Grauens (Dungeon of Horrors)||[[Belantis]]||{{flagu|Germany}}||2003||[[Vekoma]]\n|-\n|Lenny's Magic School (No rotating part)||[[Everland]]||{{flagu|South Korea}}||2007-2019 (as Rotating House) 2019||[[Mack Rides]]\n|-\n|Le D\u00e9fi de C\u00e9sar (Caesar's Challenge/The challenge of Cesar)||[[Parc Ast\u00e9rix]]||{{flagu|France}}||2008||[[Mack Rides]]\n|-\n|Alpenhotel Rasch (parts of)||- (Mobile Mad House)||{{flagu|Germany}}||2011||?\n|-\n|Maison Houdini (House Houdini)||[[Rainbow MagicLand]]||{{flagu|Italy}}||2011||[[Vekoma]]\n|-\n|[[Haunted House Monster Party]]||[[Legoland Windsor]]||{{flagu|Great Britain}}||2019||[[Vekoma]]\n|}\n\n== List of Madhouses that didn't make it. ==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Name or Area name's Madhouse !! Park !! Country !! Reason !! Manufacturer\n|-\n|Dream's Madhouse ||[[Six Flags Dubai]]||{{flagu|Dubai}}||Cancelled||[[Mack Rides]]\n|-\n|Poseidon Fury ||[[Islands of Adventure|Island of Adventure]]||{{flagu|United States}}||Project Change||[[?]]\n|-\n|El Templo de Muerte (The Temple of Dead) ||[[Bobbejaanland]]||{{flagu|Belgium}}||Unknown||[[Vekoma]]\n|-\n|Manhattan Midway's Madhouse ||[[Tokyo Disney Sea]]||{{flagu|Japan}}||Over Budget||[[Vekoma]]\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SppOrEx8DvA A video showing how a Madhouse works]\n*[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7t03Albx2_s Official trailer for Hex, a Vekoma Madhouse at Alton Towers]\n*[https://web.archive.org/w